---
title: Beef and Chickpea Stew with Charred Courgette and Garlic Bread
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Beef and Chickpea Stew in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R13_W24_UK_QR3152-50_Main_MOD_SWAP_low-180d2494.jpg
